{"tid":812152,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"我嗰FD被貴利捉左","createTime":"2018-09-09T12:07:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-09T14:56:47.000Z","uid":160146,"like":2,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c43547e3483ec54b4cc64262f6b28ce55bfe4a98","tid":812152,"uid":160146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T12:07:23.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我嗰FD衰爛賭，差貴利數被人捉左<br />\n<br />\n咁佢冇乜朋友，得我和一個痴痴呆呆的朋友陪佢女友帶著八皮野上去贖人<br />\n<br />\n上到去，條貴利大佬又唔知做乜傻笑，又玩蝴蝶刀又剩，我條痴呆FD又無啦啦大佢一百萬<br />\n<br />\n條大佬又要條痴呆FD洗牌洗條青龍出黎，條友又真的洗到出來，仲屈我7塊朱古力，想問下連登仔有乜朱古力推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8457f0b95a0161c6c97b190237fa95964f58f823","tid":812152,"uid":109690,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T12:12:38.000Z","msg":"Feodora<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1876989367083f1b2e9fbfc2c41d086c3c8bda55","tid":812152,"uid":160146,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T14:54:13.000Z","msg":"連登仔唔食朱古力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3c2cd34bb18998ade6218d46af93d40f4ac8a7d","tid":812152,"uid":40133,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T14:55:44.000Z","msg":"你朋友係咪姓陳？"},{"pid":"8318b3e1082475934b1ce6d6e6f12eaf7c1c3c08","tid":812152,"uid":160146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8457f0b95a0161c6c97b190237fa95964f58f823","tid":812152,"uid":109690,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T12:12:38.000Z","msg":"Feodora<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T14:56:15.000Z","msg":"e隻佢平時食開<br />\n又貴又苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5f5f242e2db43a4349da392f27cf78f095f77